Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是通往\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最伟大自然奇观之一的入口\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to one of the greatest of natural wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,越南韩松洞\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Hang Son Doong, in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里被认为是地球上最大的洞穴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's thought to be the largest cave on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,深达200米\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Here, 200 metres underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一年中只有几周时间\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}for just a few weeks a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光能透过洞顶的缝隙 照射入内\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}sunbeams cast light through a hole in the cave's roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这点阳光刚好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There is just enough light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能满足植物的生长\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to enable plants to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,随着继续深入\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But travel deeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗再次笼罩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and darkness returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的极端环境下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And you reach the limit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,生命如履薄冰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}of where life can exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,95)}{\fs10\fnMicrosoft YaHei\c&HD5D5D5&\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(3000,2440)}第 六 集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,120)}{\fs25\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light\c&HD5D5D5\2a&FF&\bord0\blur0\shad0\fad(3000,2440)}{\K100 }极  端  之  境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人类通常难以涉足\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}These most extreme places on our planet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些地球上最极端的环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}are often hard for us to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 这个洞穴是最近才被发现的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Indeed, this cave was only recently discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,其中蕴藏着许多惊喜\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And it contains many surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,洞穴珍珠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Cave pearls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经微小的沙粒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Once tiny sand grains,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如今足有网球大小\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}now spheres the size of tennis balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,巨大的石笋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And giant stalagmites...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,数百年来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..formed over centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,由几十亿滴水日积月累而成\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}by billions of individual drops of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,地下河在石灰岩中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Underground rivers have carved
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,开辟了这条巨大的水道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}this great passage through the limestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,长度超过8公里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Over five miles long
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,宽度足以容纳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and wide enough in places
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一架大型喷气式飞机\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to accommodate a jumbo jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而就在这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And it is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,洞穴的最深处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}in the cave's furthest chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,孕育着生命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that life can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,半透明洞穴鱼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Translucent cave fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,洞穴虾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and shrimps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,几千年来与世隔绝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Isolated for millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,仅以头顶丛林里的营养物质为生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}feeding on little more than the nutrients from the jungle above.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,洞穴鱼没有视觉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The fish are completely blind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只能依靠触觉辨认方向\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and find their way about by touch alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在这些地下世界中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}These underground worlds are at the very limit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,生命如履薄冰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}of where life can exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而在地面以上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But above ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最极端的环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}our planet's most extreme conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,非两极莫属\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}are found at the poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在北极\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Here in the north,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天的气温可以降至零下50度\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}winter temperatures can drop to -50 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一年中的四个月里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For four months of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎见不到一缕阳光\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}there is barely a glimmer of sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But here, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,生命同样有其生存之道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}life finds a way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一群北极狼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A pack of Arctic wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,浓密的皮毛提供的保护\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Their dense fur has protected them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助它们熬过了数月的严寒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}through months of bitter cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但如今阳光再次洒落大地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But now the sun is returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔斯米尔岛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is Ellesmere Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,短暂的夏季 使狼群得以重新积攒力量\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The short summer gives the wolves a chance to rebuild their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但在北极这片极端的环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But here in the Arctic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,生命举步维艰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..life is never easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,狼群的首领是一只经验丰富的雌性北极狼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This pack is led by an experienced female.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果雌狼无法带领狼群找到食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}If she can't lead them to food,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它们将很难撑过即将到来的寒冬\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the coming winter could be their last.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,猎物分散在如此广阔的区域\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Prey is spread over such a vast area
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,狼群必须不断移动\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that they must be constantly on the move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以寻找猎物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..in search of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但寻找猎物 仅仅是狩猎的第一步\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But finding prey is only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,麝牛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Musk oxen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,体型是北极狼的五倍\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They are five times the size of a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,北极狼与麝牛之间的明争暗斗由来已久\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The conflict between wolf and oxen is an ancient one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可追溯至冰河时代\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and has been waged since the Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,互相对彼此的战术都熟稔于心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Each side knows the other's tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,北极狼试图孤立\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The wolves try to isolate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,体弱幼小的麝牛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the weak or the young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一只小牛跌跌撞撞\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A calf stumbles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,狼群首领立即靠近过来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and the pack leader immediately closes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但麝牛群重整旗鼓\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But the herd regroups,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,牛角蓄势待发\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}horns at the ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,陷入僵局\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但只是短暂的僵局\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But it can only be brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,麝牛群冲向高地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This time, the herd race to higher ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当麝牛群抵达山脊顶部时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As they reach the top of the ridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性麝牛转身面向敌人以自卫\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the males turn to defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再次\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Stalemate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,陷入僵局\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,狩猎每失败一次\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Every unsuccessful hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,狼群便虚弱一分\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}leaves the pack weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,唾手可得的午餐\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This could be an easier meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但有些不对劲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But something is not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这头麝牛死于疾病\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This musk ox has died from a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,随着北极地区气候变暖\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Outbreaks like this are becoming increasingly common
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,类似的疫情变得越来越普遍\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}as the climate warms across the Arctic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管饥肠辘辘\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Despite their hunger,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,狼群还是放弃了这具尸体\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the pack don't eat this carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,新的麝牛群\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Another herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,新的机会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Another chance for the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次 北极狼驱散麝牛群\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This time, the wolves manage to split the herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,成功率得以提高\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}That may improve their chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,首领雌狼确保麝牛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The lead female makes sure that the oxen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,无法逃往山脊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}do not reach the ridge again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,随着保护的减少 小牛岌岌可危\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}With one less defender, the calf is more vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,雪中送炭\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A much-needed meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,北极狼群必须充分利用\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The wolves must continue to make the most
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,夏季的最后几周\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}of the remaining weeks of summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,从而在这片\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..so when winter returns
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最恶劣的生存环境中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..they're ready to endure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,储备能量\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}some of the harshest conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,迎接即将到来的严冬\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that exist on planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如此不宜居的极端环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Such inhospitable extremes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,并非只存在于两极\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}are not only found at the poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,随着海拔上升\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As altitude increases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,气温大幅下降\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..temperatures fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 动物同样必须充分利用季节变化\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Here, too, animals must make the most of the seasonal change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是处于繁殖季节时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Particularly if you're ready to mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,法国阿尔卑斯山\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A male common frog
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一只雄性林蛙\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}in the French Alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它整个冬天都在冰下冬眠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He has spent all winter hibernating under the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在是时候清醒过来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But now it's time to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,林蛙是变温动物 需要晒太阳来暖和起来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Being cold-blooded, he needs the sun to warm his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但几小时后一旦太阳落山\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But once it sets in a few hours' time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,林蛙便会冻死\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}he could freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 寻找伴侣迫在眉睫\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So finding a mate is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,天气不错\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The weather is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雄林蛙动身了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And he starts to sledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但竞争对手也没闲着\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But this is not a one-frog race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,数十只林蛙涌向水塘\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Dozens are rushing to the breeding pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,斜坡上爬满了林蛙\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This many frogs out on the slopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有眼睛正盯着这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..doesn't go unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,千万不能滑倒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}You can't afford any slips.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很顺利\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It was all going so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,成功抵达\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但所有雌林蛙 都已名花有主\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But all the females have already got partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个办法了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There's only one thing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,强取豪夺\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,功亏一篑\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,又一只姗姗来迟的林蛙\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Another latecomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一只雌林蛙\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A female.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真命天女会是它吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Could she be the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来得早不如来得巧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Sometimes being late can pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,煞费苦心的雄林蛙 不会让这个机会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}After all his efforts, the male is not going to let this chance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再次从指间溜走\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}slip through his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是非洲北部阿特拉斯山脉的雪松林\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the cedar forest of the Atlas Mountains, in North Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这群地中海猕猴 享受了丰收的夏季\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}These Barbary macaques enjoyed a summer of plenty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但好景不常\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but now they're paying the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的冬季刺骨严寒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Winter here can be brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,某些年 半数以上的猕猴死在了冬季\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}In some years, over half the group perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样一个社会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But in this macaque society,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,猕猴的社交能力越强\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the more social the monkey,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,生存几率便越大\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the more likely it is to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抱团取暖效果显著\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Keeping warm by huddling can make all the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不能一直抱在一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But they can't huddle all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它们为了觅食 不得不从温暖中抽身\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They must, eventually, break apart to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,猕猴四散分开 寻找食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They spread out, searching for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但到了晚上 猕猴群便会回到雪松树上挤成一团\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But each night, the group return to huddle in the cedar trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谁也不想被落下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}No-one wants to be left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是猕猴幼崽\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Especially the infants.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎的 这只猕猴幼崽跟大部队分散了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This baby, somehow, has got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它必须回到温暖的怀抱中 以维系生命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He must get back to the life-saving warmth of the huddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且必须尽快\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然而有一个问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But there is an obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一只脾气暴躁的雄猕猴对猕猴幼崽相当冷淡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A grumpy male is giving the baby a rather cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,换一种更隐蔽的方式\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Maybe a more subtle approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雄猕猴决定离开\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The male decides to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,终于\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了热情的欢迎\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..an enthusiastic reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雄弥猴则运气不佳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The male has had less luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,将是漫漫长夜等着它\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It could be a long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抱团似乎是一种表达情感的简单方式\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Huddling might seem a simple expression of affection,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于这些地中海猕猴来说 这对于生存至关重要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but among these macaques it's essential for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.16,0:25:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而这样的行为并非绝无仅有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And not just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.12,0:25:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,8000公里外的墨西哥树林中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}5,000 miles away, in the forests of Mexico,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.44,0:25:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,数百万只黑脉金斑蝶\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}monarch butterflies, in millions,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.36,0:25:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也为了生存挤作一团\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}also huddle for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.32,0:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,它们集体飞越北美大陆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}All of them have travelled across North America
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,躲避冬季的严寒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to escape the winter that is coming there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.12,0:25:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这片海拔3000米的森林\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This forest, at an altitude of 3,000 metres,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.92,0:25:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎并不能提供舒适的环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}might seem to offer little comfort...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里的气温可降至零度以下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..for temperatures here can drop below freezing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如此低温能置蝴蝶于死地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and that could kill the butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.56,0:25:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,然而事实上 树冠保有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But in fact, a thin layer of warm air
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.76,0:26:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,薄薄的一层暖空气保护着蝴蝶\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}trapped by the tree canopy protects them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只要森林不受干扰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and will do so throughout the winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.76,0:26:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就能一整个冬天为蝴蝶提供保护\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..provided that the forest remains undisturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.36,0:26:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 不可预测的极端天气\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Unpredictable extremes of weather, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.44,0:26:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会破坏这一微妙平衡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}can disrupt this delicate balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.60,0:26:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,强风吹进森林深处 降低气温\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Strong winds can push deep into the forest, chilling the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.24,0:26:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,数十万只蝴蝶\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Hundreds of thousands of butterflies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.80,0:26:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,受强风席卷 掉下树枝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}may be blown from the branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.72,0:27:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,某些年 75%冬眠中的黑脉金斑蝶死于风暴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}In some years, storms kill 75% of hibernating monarchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.00,0:27:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这只蝴蝶得以幸存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This one has survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但也掉落在地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.80,0:27:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,夜间的霜冻足以致命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And night-time frosts are fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.96,0:27:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它不能留在这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It can't stay here and live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.28,0:27:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管天气过冷 无法飞翔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It is too cold to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但它必须找个办法 回到树枝上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but it must get back into the tree branches somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.92,0:28:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它开始爬树\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So it starts to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.04,0:28:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,困难程度相当于 人类徒手爬上摩天大楼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's the equivalent of a human climbing up a skyscraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.04,0:28:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,终于安全了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Safety, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.56,0:29:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,春天来临时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As spring returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.64,0:29:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,黑脉金斑蝶从漫长的沉睡中苏醒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the monarchs wake from their long slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.60,0:29:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最伟大的自然奇观之一 就此拉开帷幕\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And now starts one of the Earth's greatest natural spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.24,0:30:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 这种集体复苏的生活习性正面临威胁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But this mass awakening is under threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.40,0:30:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,气候变化引发越来越多极端天气\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The changing climate is creating more extreme weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.12,0:30:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,风暴也越来越频繁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and storms are becoming more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但就目前而言 这一自然奇迹仍在继续\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But, for now, this miracle of nature continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.48,0:30:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.80,0:30:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不可预测且破坏力十足\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Unpredictable and destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.52,0:30:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是南非的弗因博斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is South Africa's fynbos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是地球上最植物多样化的栖息地之一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Botanically one of the most diverse habitats on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.44,0:30:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,生长着8000多种不同的植物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..with over 8,000 different plant species.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 每二十年\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Yet, every two decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.92,0:31:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾将植被焚烧殆尽\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}fire reduces the vegetation to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.88,0:31:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切看似是毁灭性的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This may seem catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但就在几天后 植物再次焕发生机\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But just days later, plants burst into life...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.76,0:31:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,重塑这片土地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and transform the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.20,0:31:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,种子与鳞茎 一直在蛰伏等待这个机会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Seeds and bulbs have been waiting for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.20,0:31:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,9000万年的进化 使部分植物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}90 million years of evolution alongside fire
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.40,0:31:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,得以适应 这片常有火灾的大地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}has made some plants so closely adapted
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.88,0:31:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于种子只有在浓烟下 才会发芽\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that they can't germinate without the presence of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,值得注意的是 地球上约50%的陆地栖息地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Remarkably, around 50% of planet Earth's terrestrial habitats
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.92,0:32:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,依靠火来维持群落健康\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}depend on fire to remain healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.08,0:32:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在澳大利亚北部 这些稀树草原需要季节性火灾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}In Northern Australia, these savannahs need seasonal fires
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.76,0:32:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才能防止森林的扩大 保持草原的开阔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to keep them open and prevent the spread of the nearby forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.12,0:32:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而对于这一多彩的居民来说\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And they are a vital habitat
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.20,0:32:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,稀树草原是重要的栖息地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}for this colourful resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.52,0:32:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,稀有的金肩鹦鹉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The rare golden-shouldered parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.52,0:32:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雄性鹦鹉 以及它终身的伴侣\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He and his lifelong partner..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.84,0:32:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,依赖于草原提供食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}rely on grassland for both food...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.64,0:32:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,以及筑巢地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and a nest site.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.52,0:33:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,金肩鹦鹉照例 将卵产在白蚁丘的洞中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As usual, they've laid their eggs in a hole in a termite mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如今育有四只雏鸟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And now there are four chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,厚厚的泥墙 不仅能保护雏鸟免受捕食者伤害\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The thick mud walls don't only protect chicks from predators,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.40,0:33:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还能遮挡烈日\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}but insulate them from the heat of the scorching sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.16,0:33:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,雏鸟羽翼渐丰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}With fledging just days away,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.32,0:33:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,金肩鹦鹉父母加班加点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the parents are working overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.68,0:33:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每天搜集成千上万枚种子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They collect thousands of seeds every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.36,0:34:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然而有一个问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But they have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.04,0:34:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾季节变得越来越不规律\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The fire season is becoming more irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.32,0:34:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果雏鸟还不会飞\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}If they are not ready to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.48,0:34:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它们将无路可逃\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}chicks have no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.24,0:35:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但选择在白蚁丘中筑巢 有着意想不到的好处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But choosing to nest in a termite mound has a surprise benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.84,0:35:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,房子可以防火\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Their home is fireproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.32,0:35:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,混泥土般的墙壁 能保护雏鸟不受火焰的伤害\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Concrete-like walls keep chicks safe from the flames outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.36,0:35:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在烧焦的土地上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The seeds of fire grass are now easier for the parrots
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,金肩鹦鹉更容易找到裂稃草的种子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to find on the blackened earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.56,0:35:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是它们最爱的食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and they are the parrots' favourite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.00,0:36:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 对于金肩鹦鹉一家来说\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So, for both adults and their fledgling chicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.96,0:36:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,熊熊烈火对于生存至关重要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..fires are essential for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.68,0:36:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但如今 它们的草原家园正在缩小\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But their grassland home is shrinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.68,0:36:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只有约1000只可爱的金肩鹦鹉幸存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and only about 1,000 of these lovely parrots still survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.28,0:36:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,通过人类对于火情的积极管理\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's through the active management of fire by humans
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.76,0:36:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,金肩鹦鹉的世界才得以存续\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}that their world now exists at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.92,0:36:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,人类活动 深刻影响着地球上的栖息地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Humans are affecting habitats across planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.64,0:36:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这对于野生动物来说\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For wildlife, all too often,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.04,0:36:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,后果往往是灾难性的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the consequences have been disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.96,0:37:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大象是耐受力最强的动物之一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Elephants are among the most tolerant of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.84,0:37:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它们十分长寿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They are very long-lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.48,0:37:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,代代相传的知识\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and knowledge passed between generations enables them
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.08,0:37:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,使大象在极端环境下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to find food and little-used sources of water in times
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.40,0:37:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能够找到食物和隐蔽的水源\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}of great environmental stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.20,0:37:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但即使如此\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But even among elephants,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.52,0:37:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大象的生存策略 如今也面临挫折\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}survival strategies are now beginning to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.80,0:37:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在肯尼亚的安博塞利 多年的极端天气\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}In Amboseli, Kenya, years of extreme weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.04,0:37:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,加上家畜的过度放牧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}combined with overgrazing by domestic cattle,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.64,0:37:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,使这片草原失去了原有的绿色\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}are turning these grasslands to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.48,0:38:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,年逾40岁的首领雌象\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This matriarch is over 40 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.84,0:38:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经历过非洲东部\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and she's already survived
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.72,0:38:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,最严重的干旱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}some of East Africa's worst droughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.88,0:38:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但今年 食物极度短缺\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But this year, food is in extremely short supply...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.20,0:38:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很难满足整个家族的需要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and her family are struggling to find enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.92,0:38:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雌象最小的孩子营养不良 身体虚弱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Her youngest son is malnourished and weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,落在家族的最后\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and is lagging behind his mother and brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.40,0:39:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雌象带领家族 来到一片熟悉的金合欢树林\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}She leads them to a pocket of acacia forest that she knows well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.36,0:39:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然而折断的树枝与倒下的树木\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But broken branches and fallen trees
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.64,0:39:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,表明其他大象已经来过此处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}show that other elephants have already been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎没剩下什么食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There is very little left worth eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.84,0:39:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,饥肠辘辘的雌象 无法分泌足够的乳汁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Without food, his mother cannot produce enough milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.92,0:39:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雌象别无选择\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}She has no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.72,0:39:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只能留下虚弱的小象\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..but to leave her weakening calf...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.92,0:39:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,前往别处寻找食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and try to find food elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.24,0:40:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 小象只能眼睁睁看着母亲与兄长\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}So, she and her elder son head off...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.40,0:40:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,离自己而去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.00,0:40:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小象只能寄希望于母亲会回来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}He can only hope for their return.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然而时间已经来不及了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But for him, time has run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.16,0:41:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,面对如此惨剧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}There is nothing his mother, or anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.48,0:42:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲也无力回天\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}could have done to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.88,0:42:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大儿子的生命还在继续\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}With her elder son still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.04,0:42:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大象家族希望尚存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}there is hope for her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.56,0:42:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是它们能迅速适应 如此极端的环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But only if they can adapt quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.16,0:42:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一些大象家族 展现出了非凡的适应力\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Some families are proving to be resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.84,0:42:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它们长途跋涉 离开安博塞利\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They're travelling long distances, away from Amboseli...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.84,0:42:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找新的食物和水源\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and finding new sources of food and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管在如此干旱的环境下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And despite the drought...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.44,0:43:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,新生命的诞生从未止步\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..calves are being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.24,0:43:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但考虑到环境变化的速度\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But given the pace of change
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.24,0:43:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以及象群面临的严峻挑战\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and the challenges they face...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.96,0:43:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟有多少非洲大象 能够适应如此极端环境\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..how many of Africa's elephants will be able to adapt?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.12,0:43:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而适应的速度又能来得及吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And can they do so fast enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.96,0:44:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,戈壁沙漠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The Gobi Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.76,0:44:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沙与雪覆盖的大地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A land of sand and snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.36,0:44:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,至少一百万年来 这里一直是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For at least a million years, this has been
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.28,0:44:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最极端的栖息地之一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}one of the most extreme habitats on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.72,0:44:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 沙子上的足印\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Yet, footprints in the sand
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.56,0:44:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,表明这里仍孕育有生命\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}reveal that there is life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.56,0:44:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,雪豹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A snow leopard.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.48,0:44:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,极其罕见\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Seldom seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.36,0:45:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是在如此炎热干旱的环境下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..especially in such hot, arid conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.56,0:45:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雪豹生存于海拔2000米以上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They live up to 2,000 metres above sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.84,0:45:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,掌控广阔的领土\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and patrol vast territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.32,0:45:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雪豹极少聚居\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They are rarely seen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.12,0:45:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一只雪豹母亲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}A mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.72,0:45:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,养育着幼崽\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..with cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.28,0:46:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是首次拍摄到\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Filmed here for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.12,0:46:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雪豹如此亲密的画面\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}in such intimate detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.96,0:46:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这使得我们得以窥见雪豹的家庭生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And they give us a glimpse of their family life...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.40,0:46:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,凡此种种\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..such as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.92,0:46:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雪豹幼崽留在母亲身边的时间\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Snow leopard cubs stay with their mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.28,0:46:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎比任何大型猫科动物都长\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}longer than those of almost any other big cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.96,0:46:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,母子相互陪伴长达两年以上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They remain together for over two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.84,0:47:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,学习在极端环境下的生存之道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..as they learn how to master the extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.04,0:47:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,使它们得以在地球上最热 最冷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Which they do so well that they are able to thrive
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.44,0:47:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,海拔最高的种种环境下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}in some of the hottest, coldest...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,茁壮成长\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..and highest places on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.60,0:47:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,数百万年的进化 使有些动物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Some animals, over millions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.48,0:47:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能够在极端恶劣的条件下生存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}have evolved ways of surviving extremely hostile conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.68,0:47:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但随着环境条件越来越极端\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}But as the extremes become more extreme...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.00,0:47:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,进化渐渐赶不上变化的速度\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..evolution is being outpaced.
