Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.08,0:53:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝 摄制组适应了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}As the days pass, the team settle into
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.20,0:53:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,地底的日常工作\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the everyday routine of life underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.64,0:54:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是脱离尘世的写照\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}This is the epitome of being off-grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.88,0:54:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫它跷跷板厕所\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}We call that one seesaw loo
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.00,0:54:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它下面有颗石头\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}because it's kind of on a rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.52,0:54:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,每次坐在上面都会后倾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and every time you sit on it and lean back,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.16,0:54:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不禁让人担心会弄得一团糟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}you're scared that there's going to be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.72,0:54:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最异样的是我们跟外界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The strangest thing is having no connection
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.16,0:54:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何联系\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to the outside world whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.24,0:54:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,生物钟彻底紊乱 地底下一切都不一样了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Time is warped. Nothing makes sense underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.24,0:54:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,开灯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Lights on!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.32,0:54:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有日光的指引 摄制组不分昼夜地工作\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Without daylight to guide them, the team work round the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.48,0:54:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄洞穴中独特的镜头\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to capture the cave's most unique features.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.16,0:54:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最特别的是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Most special of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.44,0:54:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一年中只持续几周的活动\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}an event which happens only a few weeks a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.80,0:54:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为了到达那里 他们必须穿过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}To get there, they must navigate
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.24,0:54:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,巨石区和狭窄的道路\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}through boulder fields and tight squeezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.40,0:55:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 约50万年前\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Here, around half a million years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.04,0:55:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,洞顶坍塌下来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}the cave roof collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.28,0:55:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,开启了一扇通往外界的窗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}opening a window to the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.40,0:55:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,摄制组等待合适的条件\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The team wait for just the right conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.64,0:55:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坐在这几小时了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}We've been sat here for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.24,0:55:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,最后 在右侧的墙上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}And finally, just on the right-hand side of the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.80,0:55:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,能找到光线的踪迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}we can see the first signs of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.24,0:55:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,经过数周的黑暗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}After weeks of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.60,0:55:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在200米深的地底\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}200 metres underground...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.80,0:55:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看到阳光\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..they see sunlight
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.64,0:55:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,照亮了洞穴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}illuminate the cave floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.04,0:55:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,整个巨大洞穴都被照亮了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}The way it just lights up this massive cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.88,0:55:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本来试图用四五盏灯点亮这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..when we've been trying to do it with about four or five lights
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.28,0:55:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,结果根本行不通\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}and barely even lighting the smallest section.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.72,0:55:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光照进来的时候\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}When the sun comes in, it just...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.32,0:56:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信每个人都起鸡皮疙瘩了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}I think everyone's got goose bumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.68,0:56:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这是我第一次如此感激太阳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}I don't think I've ever appreciated sun so much in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.08,0:56:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太难以置信了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.84,0:56:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看那些背光的瀑布\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Look at the backlit waterfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.88,0:56:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,坠落如此缓慢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}They're so slow coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.52,0:56:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是我见过最美好的事情之一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's literally one of the best things I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.84,0:56:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对于摄制组来说 阳光标志着\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}For the crew, the sunbeam marks a profound end
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.76,0:56:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,洞穴作业画上句号\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}to their time in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.36,0:56:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}We're outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.64,0:56:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,绿色的丛林 明媚的阳光\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's so green, it's so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.64,0:56:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,回到地面上 满满的归属感\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Being back above ground feels like where we belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.56,0:56:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,地球表面之下究竟还隐藏着\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}It's a wonder to imagine what other extremes
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.88,0:56:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的极端环境 实在是不可思议\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}still lie beneath the surface of planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.72,0:57:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.04,0:57:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,人类世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..the human world...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.92,0:57:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 动物必须探索新的方式\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..where animals must find new ways to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.96,0:57:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,与我们共存\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}..amongst us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.60,0:57:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,「栖息地探索者」生动地展现动物和它们的栖息地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs07\1c&H424242&\3c&HF0E0E1&\b1\bord1.5\shad0\}Habitat Explorer brings animals and their habitats to life.
